{"tid":2063069,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[RFI]  逮捕孟晚舟前加情報機關警告或會震撼全球","createTime":"2020-06-13T15:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T15:17:25.000Z","uid":179729,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9279630f36df533ef46180a266cd15e812ac13","tid":2063069,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"中國電訊巨頭華為首席財務官孟晚舟2018年在溫哥華轉機時被捕，引發國際關注。根據加拿大最新法庭文件顯示，在她被捕前，加拿大安全情報局（CSIS）曾擬寫報告並警告指，此舉不但會引發全球震撼，也將嚴重影響中加關係。<br />\n<br />\n法庭文件在當地時間週五被公開，包含一份由加拿大安全情報局擬寫的報告，揭示加政府牽涉2018年12月1日拘捕孟晚舟的行動。在這個已塗掉敏感信息、日期為2018年12月1日的備忘錄中，加拿大安全情報局指出，在美國聯邦調查局（FBI）建議下，於同日稍晚孟晚舟搭機抵達溫哥華國際機場時逮捕她。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20200613-%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E9%80%AE%E6%8D%95%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E5%89%8D%E5%8A%A0%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E6%A9%9F%E9%97%9C%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%88%96%E6%9C%83%E9%9C%87%E6%92%BC%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F20200613-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E9%2580%25AE%25E6%258D%2595%25E5%25AD%259F%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%2588%259F%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2597%259C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259C%2587%25E6%2592%25BC%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJopBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=6901e7f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20200613-%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E9%80%AE%E6%8D%95%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E5%89%8D%E5%8A%A0%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E6%A9%9F%E9%97%9C%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%88%96%E6%9C%83%E9%9C%87%E6%92%BC%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83</a>"},{"pid":"42d544ec5cc49ebff1682cfc18687ed815f32928","tid":2063069,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"係咪有個家鄉係中國嘅國際刑警收左皮<br />\n因為依單野收左皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" c